computation.contextfreegrammar

Class Word

  • java.lang.Object
    • computation.contextfreegrammar.Word
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<Symbol>

    public class Word
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<Symbol>
    A class for a string in our context free grammar. We use the term 'word' to refer to a string, since string is already taken in Java!
